<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="6Mar1917"><font color="red">6 March 1917</font>, <cite>Selected Letters</cite> (JJ to ANONYMOUS): Messrs Black [sic], Monro, Saw and Co wrote to me on 22 February that they had been instructed by you to forward me on 1 May, August, September and February cheques for &pound;50, making a total of &pound;200 &hellip; rheumatic iritis &hellip; As soon as I am cured I shall continue to write a novel at which I am working <cite>Ulysses</cite>.</div>
